-| Dependecies
   |- Allegro - A game programming library
      + liballeg.org
      + Debian/Ubuntu :
        sudo apt install liballegro5.2 liballegro5-dev \
                         liballegro-audio5.2 liballegro-audio5-dev \
                         liballegro-ttf5.2 liballegro-ttf5-dev

-| The code
   |- git clone https://github.com/tribula-mel/chuck.git
   |- Build :
      cd src
      make
